(Episode 7)

33
00:01:24,410 --> 00:01:26,940
Ini adalah teman SMA Jaksa Baek Joon Soo,

34
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:28,470
Shin Jang Hoon.

35
00:01:29,030 --> 00:01:30,310
Namun Jaksa Baek,

36
00:01:30,810 --> 00:01:32,920
